snippet.title: Weaponeer Worldwide Release Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST for STEAM TODAY : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2190880/WEAPONEER/

Purchase the Definitive Edition on VoxPop Games: https://store.voxpopgames.com/store/280

WEAPONEER - 
Control your character with two buttons and fight your way through 75+ levels of retro platforming that introduce new original content. You wield your sword and try to make your way back home.

Proceeds from the purchase of this title will go directly to the AbleGamers charity organization! #SoEVERYONECanGame

#everyvoicematters 

Music used under CC0: 

https://netrvnner.bandcamp.com/track/...

written on stream with the help of viewers!
www.twitch.tv/netrvnner

released August 13, 2021
